The worst case scenario is that we get denied at the center because of some stupid paperwork or procedure. Something that I didn't prepare for, or overlooked when signing up. I have $400,000, ultimately, from crypto, right now. After all taxes. It's about $10,000 a year, SWR. I can't do anything with it. I can't do anything about anything until I have 10X that number. This is stupid and crazy. I'm tired of spending so much energy thinking about it, and waiting for it. I'm drained. I've hooked up all my hope to this fantasy, and I'm empty and have nothing left. I can't keep holding forever. I don't know what I want to be over, so I can relax and start enjoying myself.
